history.content:
As a courtesy, I have once again compiled a list of webcast information about our courses. The attached google doc is intended to help crowdsource information, saving students, staff, & faculty emails regarding webcasting. It will be updated with a large delay and is subject to change.

classes.berkeley.edu continues to be the reliable place to find updates regarding faculty and courses being blocked for enrollment.

While CalCentral will allow enrollment into conflicting EECS courses, it remains the student’s responsibility to plan their schedule carefully. Departments and faculty are not required or expected to accommodate students’ schedule conflicts. Best practice is to speak to the instructors before enrolling in time conflicted classes.

If you have reliable information to add to this spreadsheet, please email me at nicolemcintyre@berkeley.edu

Spring 2019 EECS Webcast List

Any updates will be added to the spreadsheet. I will not be responding to comments requesting updates.
